About Us

Mission

Make campus storage solutions safe, simple, and secure to enhance student campus experience.

What We Do

We customize, install, and operate smart-lockers tailored to university life. We offer convenience for students and faculty.

Made By Students, For Students

Built at by University Alumni (ASU) and shaped by real campus routines. Students unlock with Univercity Unique ID Cards or Univercity login through QR code, The lockers are protected by encrypted access, steel construction, CCTV, and tamper alerts with privacy in mind. By removing mailroom lines and where do I stash this? stress, our lockers help students engage more safely and confidently in clubs, labs, classes, and campus events.

Sustainability

Our lockers are built from durable, recyclable metals with low-VOC, powder-coat finishes, and modular, repairable parts so components get replacednot whole units. Energy-efficient controllers and smart sleep modes reduce power draw, and campus-optimized routing (bookstore/IT hand-offs, after-hours pickup) helps cut repeat delivery trips. At end-of-life, we support responsible recycling and parts recovery with clear documentation for facilities teams.
Why this stands out: many vendors highlight steel = durable. We go further with repairability, energy use, and end-of-lifethe pieces students and facilities actually ask about. (Industry discussions increasingly connect smart lockers with lower delivery emissions and recyclable construction.)

Frequently Asked Questions

Please reach us at aj3brac@gmail.com if you cannot find an answer to your question.

What is the minimum rental period for a unit?
The minimum rental is 1 hour, and we charge by the hour. Time is billed in 1-hour increments.
What fits in a locker?
We offer three common sizes on campus. Use these as a guideexact interior space is shown in the app when you reserve.
  • Small ~ 12" W 15" D 18" H ( 30 38 46 cm) Fits: laptop + textbooks, backpack, purse, small packages, lab kit, camera bag.
  • Medium ~ 15" W 18" D 24" H ( 38 46 61 cm) Fits: large backpack, gym bag, 1517" laptop with case, stack of books, shoe boxsize parcels, violin/ukulele case.
  • Large ~ 18" W 22" D 34" H ( 46 56 86 cm) Fits: duffel, small carry-on suitcase, multiple packages, art tubes/portfolios, skateboard (short/mini).
Do you offer any discounts for long-term rentals?
Yes, we offer discounts for customers who rent for six months or longer. Please contact our office for more details.
Are there any limits or Items I can Store?
Max item weight ~40 lbs (18 kg) per locker. For safety and policy compliance, no food that requires refrigeration, liquids that can spill, cash/IDs, hazardous/flammable materials (including batteries leaking/acid), weapons, illegal substances, or living things. If youre unsure, check the in-app list before reserving.
